aS'Fusion is the process that powers active or "main sequence" stars.The fusion of two nuclei with lower masses than iron (which, along with nickel, has the largest binding energy per nucleon) generally releases energy, while the fusion of nuclei heavier than iron absorbs energy.'
p7130
aS'The opposite is true for the reverse process, nuclear fission.'
p7131
