p7389
aS'Hence TP53 is classified as a tumor suppressor gene.'
p7390
aS'The name p53 was given in 1979 describing the apparent molecular mass; SDS-PAGE analysis indicates that it is a 53-kilodalton (kDa) protein.'
p7391
aS'However, the actual mass of the full length p53 protein (p53a) based on the sum of masses of the amino acid residues is only 43.7 kDa.'
p7392
