aS"Many of its characteristics (comedic prose; themes of sexual desire and sexual frustration; a self-conscious literariness) went on to become Roth trademarks.In 1998, the Modern Library ranked Portnoy's_Complaint 52nd on its list of the 100 best English-language novels of the 20th century."
