aS'The story is set in the Late Middle Ages, during the reign of Louis XI (1461-1483). Background Victor_Hugo began writing The_Hunchback_of_Notre-Dame in 1829, largely to make his contemporaries more aware of the value of the Gothic architecture, which was neglected and often destroyed to be replaced by new buildings, or defaced by replacement of parts of buildings in a newer style.'
