aS'The_Night_Watch is a world renowned example of Baroque art. Key elements The painting is renowned for three characteristics: its colossal size (363 cm x 437 cm (11.91 ft x 14.34 ft)), the effective use of light and shadow (chiaroscuro), and the perception of motion in what would have traditionally been a static military portrait.The painting was completed in 1642, at the peak of the Dutch Golden Age.'
